Name: UCSB
Description: A great university located along the California coast!

Name: Rio Hondo Golf Club
Description: A golf course which I frequented during quarantine with a friend, allowing me to pursue a new hobby in golfing.

Name: Allegiant Stadium
Description: New stadium in which my favorite football team, the Las Vegas Raiders, now plays. I hope to catch a game one day.

Name: Eiffel Tower
Description: Famous tower in Paris, a place which I visited on a school trip my junior year of high school. One of the few monuments/landmarks that lives up to the hype.

Name: Dodger Stadium
Description: The stadium which my favorite baseball team, the Los Angeles Dodgers, plays in. I have plenty of memories here from seeing lots of games growing up.

Name: Sunset Beach
Description: A beach I frequented when I was living back home. I enjoyed that it was tucked away in a neighborhood, so it was always relatively lowkey.
